1-1 Hoffenheim; Schalke 2-0 Bayern Munich; Bayer Leverkusen 3-2
Cologne; Nuremberg 0-2 Borussia Dortmund.  France: Lens 1-1 Auxerre; Rennes 1-0 Monaco; Sochaux 2-1
